            <div class="course-content">
                <h2>Become a Backend Developer</h2>
                <p>
                    Backend development focuses on server-side programming that powers
                    web applications. This comprehensive course will teach you how to
                    create robust, scalable, and secure backend systems.
                </p>

                <h3>Course Overview</h3>
                <p>
                    In this intensive 12-week program, you'll learn all the essential
                    skills needed to become a professional backend developer, from
                    database design to API development and server management.
                </p>

                <h3>What You'll Learn</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Server-side programming languages (Node.js, Python, Java)</li>
                    <li>Database design and management (SQL and NoSQL)</li>
                    <li>RESTful API development</li>
                    <li>Authentication and authorization</li>
                    <li>Server deployment and management</li>
                    <li>Performance optimization</li>
                    <li>Security best practices</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Course Structure</h3>
                <p>
                    The course is divided into modules, each focusing on a specific
                    aspect of backend development:
                </p>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Foundations:</strong> Understanding web architecture and
                        server-client communication
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Programming:</strong> Deep dive into server-side languages
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Databases:</strong> Data modeling, retrieval, and
                        manipulation
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>APIs:</strong> Design and implementation of RESTful
                        services
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Authentication:</strong> User management and security
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Deployment:</strong> Server setup and application hosting
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Final Project:</strong> Building a complete backend system
                    </li>
                </ol>

                <h3>Prerequisites</h3>
                <p>
                    Basic programming knowledge is recommended but not required. Our
                    course starts with fundamentals and gradually progresses to advanced
                    topics.
                </p>


